In the 2nd district on Kilincs street a 310 sqm, 6-roomed, mechanized, american kitchen, panoramic, with balcony, garage, renovated, sauna, 4-storey garden-friendly, pet friendly semi-detached house for rent.

The cost of housing is about 50,000 HUF per month, but it also depends on consumption.
The property is subject to negotiation. Pet friendly and outdoors can be smoked.
In the basement of the house there is a garage and a sauna.
The house has 3 baths + wc, plus a separate toilet.
On the first floor there are 2 balconies and on the ground floor there is a huge terrace.

Minimum rental period is 1 year!
The house can be moved immediately by paying a 2 month deposit and the rent for the month.
column14:
In District 2, on Tarkony Street, a 300 sqm, furnished, mechanized, renovated 3 storey, huge garden with two balconies, 8 rooms, 200 meters from a French school, 2 garages, 3 courtyard, kitchen, 3 bathrooms, fireplace, dog running, underfloor heating, solar collector, rentable from January to rent. 

The cost of housing is not too high because it has modern thermal insulation on the house and thermal insulation windows are installed and on top there are solar collectors. 
Pet Friendly House. Smoking outside the house is possible only! 
Optional, even unfurnished. 

Minimum rental period is 1 year. 
The house can be moved from January by paying a 2 month deposit and the rent for the current month.
column18:

Floor: Corridor, bath with toilet 3 separate bedrooms, wardrobe. The entire house is insulated with large, grassy garden. The apartment is furnished and unmechanisation. (kitchen furniture, gas cooker) Freshly painted and with quality, very nice coverings and special solutions.  Move in: immediately possible.
column24: Csatárka quite green environment in horizontal landscaped garden 3-storey renovated, luxury family house is available for a minimum of one year rent. Upstairs there are 2 separate bedrooms, second living room and bathroom with shower. column35: In Budapest, in a quiet area of the 3rd district in Taborhegy, Jablonka road a 280sqm detached house is available for rent on 3 levels.
column37:
Full house with garden next to Margaret bridge for rent in January-February

€ 500

In the central part of Buda, a few minutes away from the Margaret Bridge our beloved little house with garden is for rent. At the beginning of Pusztaszeri street, at the famous Daubner confectionery, a 42 m2 renovated, mechanized, stylishly furnished house. From 9 January can be moved for approx. two months (dates are negotiable).

Living room (15 m2), bedroom (10 m2), separate kitchen (10 m2), bathroom. Stylish, handmade furniture, terrace, peaceful garden.

Transportation: 4/6 tram in a 10 minutes walk or two tram / bus stops. The new Buda trams in a few minutes. Buda hills are in a few bus stops.
Restaurants, shops, market at Kolosy square, a few minutes from the house. Several baths, including the famous Lukács bath, are just around.

Monthly rental fee: 500 EUR (150.000 HUF), invoice is available. Monthly costs, including circulation heating, electricity, communal costs, water and wi-fi: 100 EUR (30.000 HUF). You can book it any time for one month rental fee and one month deposit.
